    "about_this_item": "<div class=\"dm-tabs__rte\" style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent; color:#2a211b; font-family:inherit;\">\n  <div style=\"display:grid; gap:16px; margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:16px 18px; border-radius:16px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.055); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10);\">\n      <div style=\"margin:0 0 6px; color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; line-height:1; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase;\">\n        Sculptural Wood Media Console\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n        Create a stylish listening corner with this modern wooden record stand, featuring a spacious top surface for a turntable and a dedicated storage area for vinyl records and audio gear.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">\n        01\n      </span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Solid Wood Handcrafted Feel\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          The flowing curved shelves, rounded edges, raised legs, and rich wood grain give this piece a premium handcrafted feel, making it a statement furniture piece for your room.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">\n        02\n      </span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Smart Record & Media Storage\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          The right-side cabinet section is ideal for organizing vinyl records upright, while the upper compartment can hold a receiver or media accessories.\n        </p>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:7px; margin:0; padding:0;\">\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">\n            Vinyl Records\n          </span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">\n            Turntable\n          </span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">\n            Audio Gear\n          </span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">\n        03\n      </span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Flexible Size Options\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          Available in multiple dimensions to give you flexible options for small spaces, larger music setups, or statement display areas in your living room.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
